{
  "texts": [
    "Firstly, our approach is solely qualitative and does not incorporate quantitative data, limiting the depth of our analysis and the generalizability of our findings.",
    "Secondly, one potential limitation is the size of the text corpus analyzed.",
    "The final corpus consisted of 166 answers to 17 questions.",
    "While this may seem small, it is in line with recommendations for thematic analysis, as 100-200 items is a sufficient sample size for a small-scale thematic analysis project [98].",
    "Given the exploratory nature of this study and the emerging nature of the deepfake phenomenon, the sample size is appropriate for the research objectives."
  ]
}